<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title><%= title %></title>

  <style>
    * {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      box-sizing: border-box;
      font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;
    }

    body {
      background-color: #f4f6f9;
      color: #333;
    }

    /* Header */
    .header {
      background-color: #2c3e50;
      color: #fff;
      padding: 15px 30px;
    }

    .header h2 {
      font-weight: normal;
    }

    /* Layout */
    .container {
      display: flex;
    }

    /* Sidebar */
    .sidebar {
      width: 220px;
      background-color: #34495e;
      min-height: 100vh;
      padding-top: 20px;
    }

    .sidebar a {
      display: block;
      color: #ecf0f1;
      padding: 12px 20px;
      text-decoration: none;
      border-bottom: 1px solid #2c3e50;
    }

    .sidebar a:hover {
      background-color: #2c3e50;
    }

    /* Content */
    .content {
      flex: 1;
      padding: 30px;
    }

    .content h3 {
      color: rgb(56, 46, 7);
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }

    .about-box {
      background-color: #fff;
      padding: 25px;
      max-width: 700px;
      border-radius: 6px;
      box-shadow: 0 2px 6px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
      margin-top: 20px;
    }

    .about-box p {
      margin-bottom: 14px;
      line-height: 1.6;
      font-size: 15px;
    }
  </style>
</head>

<body>

  <!-- Header -->
  <div class="header">
    <h2>Hotel Management Dashboard</h2>
  </div>

  <div class="container">

    <!-- Sidebar -->
    <div class="sidebar">
      <a href="/">Dashboard</a>
      <a href="/about">About Us</a>
      <a href="/contact">Contact</a>
      <a href="/contact-us">Contact Us</a>
    </div>

    <!-- Main Content -->
    <div class="content">
      <h3>Welcome to About Us Page</h3>
      <p>Learn more about who we are and how we serve our guests.</p>

      <div class="about-box">
        <p>
          Founded with a commitment to comfort and care, our hotel has always
          believed that hospitality is more than a serviceâ€”it is a tradition.
        </p>
        <p>
          From warm welcomes at the front desk to thoughtfully managed rooms,
          our team works every day to ensure a smooth and memorable stay.
        </p>
        <p>
          This dashboard helps us manage operations efficiently while keeping
          the guest experience at the heart of everything we do.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

  </div>

</body>
</html>



